{"tid":1163890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日香港人幾時先醒","createTime":"2019-05-20T17:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T18:17:36.000Z","uid":102347,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ada6a577b08e087caf8df6aaaef1c0ac562f8232","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"就以4000蚊為例子<br />\n全香港人都比陳茂波條撚樣撚到香港人<br />\n點解今時今日仲未有人叫條垃圾落台？<br />\n其他國家一早已經出黎遊行叫條陳茂波拎返個位出黎<br />\n點解香港人仲要受條撚樣氣<br />\n果4000蚊 唔係政府架<br />\n係我地班納稅人架<br />\n點解我地唔出黎抵抗 <br />\n叫佢加快腳步？ <br />\n佢咁少事都做唔黎<br />\n香港人既錢點交比呢個人？<br />\n派錢都派唔到<br />\n咁不如叫佢讓個位出黎比其他人做<br />\n我唔信全港人企出黎<br />\n叫佢落台 我唔信無效<br />\n我地一直比人恰到上心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34138decd80bf3c25f9ce767e6946caf83f1fb25","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"香港科技落後仲要用人手填資料<br />\n已經係世界笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05d382760ec673aafa634cef2a48db20830fca5","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"大家有無諗過<br />\n果4000$<br />\n根本係拖到貿貿然戰打完（雖然唔知幾時完）<br />\n先會加快進度比我地班香港人？"},{"pid":"7181f6ec9bf18f975a4e565e943162f8ee881e03","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"香港人 駁唔到？"},{"pid":"1970f3c36ea06fe2e87355b8d7e5fad94f203873","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed90b03beff69bc3b9c6a2b5e7e8dfa77c97ae2","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93340fdc3d468c3d5658cab75252654a67245fa","tid":1163890,"uid":102347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy